title: Grateful Dead - Fillmore East 1970 January + September
description:
Grateful Dead
Fillmore East, NYC, 1970

2 excellent sets - 2 hours 12 minutes 21 seconds altogether

Disc 1
January 2, 1970

01 Dark Star (fades after 29:45)
02 We Join St. Stephen Already In Progress (at "Lady finger dipped in moonlight")
03 The Eleven
04 Turn On Your Lovelight

Disc 2
September 19, 1970

01 Dark Star
02 St. Stephen
03 Not Fade Away
04 Turn On Your Lovelight

Soundboard recordings downloaded from2005 - Saved VBR stream, converted to FLAC for editing.  Fixed up by Zoticus using Wavepad. Stitched over drop-outs, splices, etc., repaired volume fluctuations among files and saved as FLAC, then burned to CD-R.

These files ripped from CD-R to FLAC with Winamp.
